OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784380679
OL,3,CSouth East Water raises doubts over
OL,4,Cfuture survival without fresh financing
OL,6,FSouth East Water has warned that it
OL,7,Fneeds to secure fresh financing to
OL,8,Fstay afloat after taking a #55 million
OL,9,Fhit from outages over the winter.
OL,11,FThe water supplier to around 2.3
OL,12,Fmillion customers in the south east of
OL,13,FEngland said it was in discussions
OL,14,Fwith lenders to agree a new loan
OL,15,Ffacility.
OL,17,FIt has enough cash to keep going until
OL,18,FJuly 2027 but flagged that "shortly
OL,19,Fafter" it will need to get more
OL,20,Ffinancing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
