OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784380679
OL,3,CSouth East Water raises doubts over
OL,4,Cfuture survival without fresh financing
OL,6,FThe company said in its annual report:
OL,7,F"Shortly after the going concern
OL,8,Fperiod it will be necessary to secure
OL,9,Fnew loan facilities in order to
OL,10,Fcontinue as a going concern.
OL,12,F"The severe but plausible downside
OL,13,Fcase... would indicate a need for
OL,14,Ffurther financing towards the end of
OL,15,Fthe financial year."
OL,17,FThis means that there are doubts over
OL,18,Fthe company's ability to continue
OL,19,Foperating as a result of its financial
OL,20,Fwoes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784380679
OL,3,CSouth East Water raises doubts over
OL,4,Cfuture survival without fresh financing
OL,6,FBut the company said talks with
OL,7,Flenders over new financing to support
OL,8,Fits major infrastructure investment
OL,9,Fprogramme are in the late stages and
OL,10,Fare expected to conclude over the
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,FSouth East Water said the last
OL,14,Ffinancial year had been a "tough year
OL,15,Foperationally and financially".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
