OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784380679
OL,3,CSouth East Water raises doubts over
OL,4,Cfuture survival without fresh financing
OL,6,F"The operational challenges of the
OL,7,F2025 summer drought and the two major
OL,8,Fincidents in December 2025 and January
OL,9,F2026 resulted in significant
OL,10,Fadditional costs, with the incident
OL,11,Fcosts amounting to #54.7 million in
OL,12,Fcompensation to customers and other
OL,13,Fcosts such as bottled water and
OL,14,Ftankering costs."
OL,16,FIt is referring to supply
OL,17,Finterruptions in Tunbridge Wells and
OL,18,Facross Kent and Sussex during the
OL,19,Fwinter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
