FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784380679
OL,3,CSouth East Water raises doubts over
OL,4,Cfuture survival without fresh financing
OL,6,FThe supplier said more than 77,000
OL,7,Fcustomers experienced "periods without
OL,8,Fwater supply, low pressure or
OL,9,Fintermittent supplies" as a result of
OL,10,Fleaks and bursts across the network
OL,11,Fand storms causing power cuts.
OL,13,FSchools were closed and some customers
OL,14,Fhad to cancel work due to childcare
OL,15,Fissues while others had difficulty
OL,16,Fdealing with medical conditions,
OL,17,Faccording to regulator Ofwat.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
