OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784380679
OL,3,CSouth East Water raises doubts over
OL,4,Cfuture survival without fresh financing
OL,6,FSouth East Water's shareholders are
OL,7,Falso funding a #30.5 million redress
OL,8,Fpackage agreed with Ofwat that will go
OL,9,Ftowards improving the network in the
OL,10,Faffected local areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
